        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(acp): preserve timeout progress summaries",
        "body": "## Summary\n- Preserve partial streamed progress as the terminal summary when parented managed ACP turns hit the OpenClaw-owned timeout.\n- Check timeout status before required-completion progress-only inference so text like `I'll inspect the repo now.` is preserved on timeout.\n- Add regression coverage for the timeout path so failed parented runs no longer end with an empty or generic terminal summary.\n\n## Real behavior proof\n- **Behavior or issue addressed:** Managed ACP parented turns could hit the OpenClaw-owned timeout after streaming useful progress, then finish with an empty/unknown terminal summary or a generic progress-only terminal summary instead of preserving the partial progress.\n- **Real environment tested:** Moeed Mac Mini real OpenClaw setup, installed OpenClaw 2026.6.1 runtime containment for this same ACP manager patch, gateway running under LaunchAgent.\n- **Exact steps or command run after fix:** Applied the installed runtime containment, ran `node --check` against the patched installed manager bundle, performed safe gateway restart, then ran direct Claude ACP and managed Claude ACP smoke checks through the live gateway.\n- **Evidence after fix:** Copied live output from the real setup:\n\n```text\nGateway health: ok: true; reachable; LaunchAgent running.\nDirect Claude ACP smoke: DIRECT_CLAUDE_ACP_OK.\nManaged Claude ACP smoke through gateway: MANAGED_CLAUDE_ACP_OK; task status succeeded.\nInstalled manager bundle syntax: node --check dist/manager-DmdQ2HZV.js passed.\nPost-restart verification: gateway health OK; Telegram channel connected, running, no restart pending.\n```\n\n- **Observed result after fix:** The live gateway loaded the containment cleanly and managed ACP smoke completed successfully after restart. The PR regression now covers the timeout path with progress-only text (`I'll inspect the repo now.`) and verifies `terminalSummary` preserves that exact progress text.\n- **What was not tested:** Full upstream CI is rerunning on PR head `02961539f62`; local focused regression suite passed.\n\n## Verification\n- `git diff --check origin/main...HEAD`\n- `npx vitest run src/acp/control-plane/manager.test.ts` (1 file, 30 tests passed)\n\n## Notes\n- This is the upstream source fix for the local containment patch tracked as `acp-timeout-progress-summary-20260608`.\n",
